{"title":"Bike of the Week | Brompton x Bear Grylls collaboration trades commuting for camping","link":"https://www.bikeradar.com/features/bike-of-the-week/brompton-x-bear-grylls-c-line-expore/","date":1696431607000,"content":"<img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/BxBG-f323124.png?quality=90&amp;resize=620,413\" srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/BxBG-f323124.png?quality=45&amp;resize=1440,959 1440w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/BxBG-f323124.png?quality=45&amp;resize=1200,799 1200w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/BxBG-f323124.png?quality=90&amp;resize=960,639 960w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/BxBG-f323124.png?quality=90&amp;resize=720,479 720w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/BxBG-f323124.png?quality=90&amp;resize=576,383 576w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/BxBG-f323124.png?quality=90&amp;resize=360,239 360w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/BxBG-f323124.png?quality=90&amp;resize=180,119 180w\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore 'Bike of the Week' banner\" title=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore 'Bike of the Week' banner\" />                                            <p>First spotted at Eurobike 2023, the Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore has Tarzan-swung its way to BikeRadar HQ.</p>\n<p>This special edition folding bike was made in collaboration with the adventurer and TV personality, and it’s complete with a woodland-inspired paintjob and matching bags to commute or head into the bush.</p>\n<p>Brompton is hoping the collaboration inspires its customers to ride outside of the city, although it still has all the handy commuting trinkets for <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/fitness-and-training/cycling-to-work-guide/\">cycling to work</a>.</p>\n<h2>Matching British woodlands</h2>\n<div>\n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n    <img width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore\" title=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore\" />\n\n</div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> A Brompton for the great outdoors?</span></figcaption><span> <i>Steve Sayers / Our Media </i></span></div>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-folding-bikes/\">folding bike</a>’s frame is Moss Green with what Brompton calls a Mushroom Grey fork, rear triangle and handlebar stem.</p>\n<p>Brompton says it decided on these colours because they match the natural tones of the British woodland and the matte finish gives the bike a muted appearance.</p>\n<p>The dual colourway is livened up with Adventure Orange graphics.</p>\n<div>\n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n    <img width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls handlebar bag\" title=\"12-21-04_SNY0018\" />\n\n</div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> The handlebar bag has a small 1L capacity.</span></figcaption><span> <i>Steve Sayers / Our Media </i></span></div>\n<p>The colour scheme continues on the two special edition, waterproof bags, which are also Moss Green with orange zips and come included with the bike.</p>\n<p>The smaller 1L <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-bike-handlebar-bags/\">handlebar bag</a> can double up as a <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-saddle-bags/\">saddlebag</a>.</p>\n<p></p><div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure>\n<div>\n    \n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \n        <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/BR8298-a0fb36d.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" width=\"556\" height=\"723\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls Waterproof Backpack\" title=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls Waterproof Backpack\" />\n</div>    <figcaption>\n        <div>\n    <figcaption>\n        <span>The Waterproof Backpack is also available separately for £180.</span>\n    </figcaption>\n    <span>\n                    <i>Oscar Huckle / Our Media </i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure>\n<div>\n    \n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \n        <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/BR8301-257144b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" width=\"556\" height=\"723\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls Waterproof Backpack\" title=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls Waterproof Backpack\" />\n</div>    <figcaption>\n        <div>\n    <figcaption>\n        <span>The orange zip matches the frame’s graphics. </span>\n    </figcaption>\n    <span>\n                    <i>Oscar Huckle / Our Media </i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure>\n<div>\n    \n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \n        <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/BR8303-fa4235b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" width=\"556\" height=\"723\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls Waterproof Backpack\" title=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls Waterproof Backpack\" />\n</div>    <figcaption>\n        <div>\n    <figcaption>\n        <span>The shoulder straps are made from hi-density foam. </span>\n    </figcaption>\n    <span>\n                    <i>Oscar Huckle / Our Media </i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\nThere is also a special edition 17-litre Brompton x Bear Grylls Waterproof Backpack, which can be used as a main bag and mounts onto the front carrier block.\n<section>\n    <div>\n        \n<h3>What is Bike of the Week?</h3>\n<p>Every fortnight, we’ll bring you a detailed first look at one of the latest bikes (or framesets) to arrive at BikeRadar HQ – from road to commuting, gravel to enduro, and anything in between.</p>\n<p>This is our chance to introduce the bike and everything that makes it unique before hitting the road or trails.</p>\n<p>Head to our <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/features/bike-of-the-week/\">Bike of the Week hub</a> for previous editions.</p>\n<p>\n\n    </p></div>\n    </section>\n\n<h2>A familiar recipe under the hood</h2>\n<div>\n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n    <img width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore\" title=\"12-20-12_SNY0012\" />\n\n</div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> 6 gears is the most Brompton offers.</span></figcaption><span> <i>Steve Sayers / Our Media </i></span></div>\n<p>Underneath the paintjob lies a fairly typical Brompton C Line Explore, which is designed to “commute, travel and run errands in style”.</p>\n<p>The hand-brazed steel frame has a 6-speed <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/drivetrains-explained-all-of-the-parts-that-make-your-bike-go/\">drivetrain</a>. The drivetrain consists of a 50t front chainring paired with two cogs and a three-speed <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/internal-gear-hubs/\">internal gear hub</a>.</p>\n<div>\n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n    <img width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore\" title=\"12-21-28_SNY0023\" />\n\n</div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> X marks the spot.</span></figcaption><span> <i>Steve Sayers / Our Media </i></span></div>\n<p>Brompton specs the Bear Grylls bike with its M-type handlebar, which sits between the taller H-type bar and flat S-type bar.</p>\n<div>\n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n    <img width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore\" title=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore\" />\n\n</div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> The Brooks C17 Cambium saddle is a plush upgrade from the standard C Line Explore saddle.</span></figcaption><span> <i>Steve Sayers / Our Media </i></span></div>\n<p>The bike features a Brooks C17 Cambium black <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-bike-saddles/\">saddle</a> and you can choose between a standard or telescoping <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/seatposts/\">seatpost</a> at the point of purchase. Brompton recommends its telescopic seatpost for taller riders, which offers an extra 6cm of saddle height.</p>\n<p>Brompton says the 16inx35mm Schwalbe Marathon Racer tyres are capable on roads and light gravel. The tan wall tyres complement the bike’s orange graphics nicely.</p>\n<div>\n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n    <img width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore\" title=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore\" />\n\n</div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> The bike comes with tan wall tyres and mudguards.</span></figcaption><span> <i>Steve Sayers / Our Media </i></span></div>\n<p>Although the frameset features brazings for a Brompton <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-bike-pump/\">mini pump</a> (these are manufactured by Zefal or Lezyne), the bike doesn’t come with one.</p>\n<p>You do, however, get <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-mudguards-fenders-a-buyers-guide/\">mudguards</a> to protect you from the elements and a bell on the handlebar to signal your presence to any predators.</p>\n<div>\n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n    <img width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Oscar Huckle riding Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore\" title=\"Oscar Huckle riding Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore\" />\n\n</div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> Like the celebrity, the Brompton adapts to its habitat.</span></figcaption><span> <i>Steve Sayers / Our Media </i></span></div>\n<p>The bike retails for £1,895 and weighs 12.04kg.</p>","author":"Oscar Huckle","siteTitle":"BikeRadar","siteHash":"df99dd1320fcd97327a2def4c67247c08cd4090a7dab684a0eddb9b856f80ef1","entryHash":"0292da5d8a2655d279cc6767b4145f8baf68a5c512fd4c1f50c75a03be54e9f7","category":"Cycling"}